| Operation   | Average Time | Worst Case (Skewed Tree) |
|-------------|--------------|---------------------------|
| Search      |   O(log N)   |        O(N)               |
| Insertion   |   O(log N)   |        O(N)               |
| Deletion    |   O(log N)   |        O(N)               |
| Inorder Traversal | O(N)   |        O(N)               |

(ğŸ”¸ Balanced BSTs like AVL or Red-Black Trees keep time close to O(log N))

